Name: I AM FLY
About the game: A fly lives a short time, so collect poop and become a fat fly! OR Eat rotten poop and die before you are satisfied! Features: Easy To Play Humorous Gameplay Fly Till You Die Realistic Graphics Steam Integration (Achivements, Leaderboards, Etc.) ~Tips~ There are 3 types of poops: Regular (Brown) - Good To Eat Rotten (Yellow) - Causes Damage Surprise (Purple) - Invincibility for a limited time
